CatDescriptText: The inscriptions on trophies read: "College All-Stars, Syracuse Nationals, October 22, 1955, Most Valuable All-Star Player," and "Maurice Stokes....donated by Alpha Phi Delta....St. John Bosco Apostle of Youth, Outstanding Athlete 1954-1955."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing dark suit and light colored collar, exchanging small document with man wearing dark suit, in domestic interior with built-in china cabinet, woven patterned wallpaper, and mantle with trophies, including trophy clock inscribed to Maurice Stokes reading 12:22
